reviewText: would like to get it in dvd
It was his last starring role but it may well have been his very best.  Great movie!!!
My mother had been looking for this movie for a long time as is is a huge Roy Rogers fan.  I was so happy to find it for her and she was tickled to have it!

If you actually want to get this video just go to [...].com and go to the contact us page. You will be able to purchase it from there. Hope you get some enjoyment out of the movie. It is one of my parents' favorite movies and they really enjoyed it.
